'''Dr. Marks''' is a doctor who took care of [[Saul]] before his death.

==History==
Dr. Marks was caring for Saul during his time on hospice care for end-stage heart failure. When he flatlined while Levi was visiting, she came in and confirmed that he was gone.

==Career==
She's a doctor at Olympia Meadows.
